WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.500
Hello! In this video I'll show you how to rent a portable charger (power bank).

00:05.500 --> 00:13.000
First, open the phone camera and scan the station's QR Code — you'll go straight to our website.

00:13.000 --> 00:18.000
The next step is to tap "Agree and rent".

00:18.000 --> 00:22.000
Enter your phone number and tap "Send".

00:22.000 --> 00:24.000
Fill in the captcha as well.

00:24.000 --> 00:29.000
You'll receive a verification code by SMS.

00:29.000 --> 00:34.000
Then you'll be logged into your account, where you can choose between two payment methods.

00:34.000 --> 00:37.000
PIX or credit card.

00:37.000 --> 00:44.000
PIX is the fastest option because the system generates a copy-and-paste QR Code.

00:44.000 --> 00:53.000
When you pick PIX, enter your name and your PIX key (where the refund will be sent).

00:53.000 --> 01:00.000
After filling that in, the system generates the QR Code — copy and paste it.

01:00.000 --> 01:03.000
Open your bank app and complete the payment.

01:03.000 --> 01:11.000
Once the PIX clears, the station detects the payment and the power bank is automatically ejected.

01:11.000 --> 01:14.000
Pickup complete.

01:14.000 --> 01:17.000
Remember that all the cables are stored on the back of the power bank.

01:17.000 --> 01:22.000
Pick the one you need and charge your phone.

01:22.000 --> 01:27.000
After using it, when you're ready to return it,

01:27.000 --> 01:35.000
you can return it at the same station or any other station in the city — just plug it back in.

01:35.000 --> 01:40.000
When you return it, the station detects it automatically.

01:40.000 --> 01:42.000
Return complete.

01:42.000 --> 01:44.000
The refund hits your PIX instantly.
